Package: ialctl
Version: 3.11.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: IAL Team <ial@example.com>
Description: IAL Infrastructure Assistant - CLI Tool
 Infrastructure as Language (IAL) command-line interface
 with automatic IAL to CloudFormation conversion and
 placeholder substitution fixes.
 .
 Features:
 - Automatic IAL metadata to CloudFormation conversion
 - Fixed placeholder substitution ([VPC_ID] -> CloudFormation Ref)
 - Unified CLI and interactive interfaces
 - Complete phase lifecycle management (create/deploy/delete)
 - Idempotent deployments with cleanup
